  "name": "Guiding Bolt",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/light/projectile-beam-yellow.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A flash of light streaks toward a creature of your choice within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes <strong>4d6 radiant damage</strong>, and the next attack roll made against this target before the end of your next turn has <strong>advantage</strong>, thanks to the mystical dim light glittering on the target until then.</p>\n<p><em><h3>At Higher Levels</h3></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 1st.</p>",
